overview.en: D Community is a group of young people based on blockchain technology, through the chain upgrade of the famous secondary brand platform Dilidili. The rapidly growing user scale and rich realized scenarios of di li li allow D Community to build its planned ecology with ideal efficiency. D currently has 30 million to 40 million monthly active users. In the future, D Community is not only a community of young people, but also a powerful traffic engine of blockchain industry.
overview.zh: D社是基于区块链技术的年轻人社群集合体，通过对著名二次品牌平台《嘀哩嘀哩》链化升级而来。《嘀哩嘀哩》快速成长的用户规模与丰富的已实现场景，可以让D社在建设自身规划的生态时拥有理想的效率。D社目前的月活跃用户在3000万到4000万之间。在未来，D社不仅是年轻人的社群集合，同时也是区块链行业强大的流量引擎。
